<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sincerely-adv">sincerely <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sɪn'sɪəli/    美 /sɪn'sɪrli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>真诚地；诚实地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I sincerely hope your father will be well again soon.
我真诚地希望你父亲早日康复。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I sincerely hope you could join us.
我真诚地希望你能加入我们。</p><footer>2017 全国书面表达</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="yours-sincerely">(yours) sincerely</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[用于正式信件末尾] 敬上； 谨上</strong>  </p></div>